{"type":"data","nodes":[{"type":"data","data":[{"debug":1},true],"uses":{}},{"type":"data","data":[{"zotero":1,"inscriptions":5},{"title":2,"date":3,"citation":4},"Das Femininum von ἥρως","1927","\u003Cspan>P. Kretschmer, ‘Das Femininum von ἥρως’, \u003Ci>Glotta\u003C/i> 16, no. 3–4 (1927): 306–7\u003C/span>",[6,115,160,200],{"file":7,"uri":7,"title":8,"status":9,"editionAuthor":11,"type":12,"objectType":16,"material":20,"condition":24,"layoutDesc":25,"handNote":31,"date":43,"places":48,"geo":57,"country":61,"region":62,"settlement":54,"repository":63,"idno":67,"textLang":69,"facsimile":73,"provenance":50,"letterHeights":80,"publications":81,"zotero":89,"keywords":97,"html":107,"bibl":108},"ISic001550","I.Sicily inscription 001550",{"_":10},"draft",null,{"_":13,"ana":14,"ref":15},"funerary","#function.funerary","http://www.eagle-network.eu/voc/typeins/lod/92.html",{"_":17,"ana":18,"ref":19},"aedicula","#object.aedicula","http://www.eagle-network.eu/voc/objtyp/lod/180.html",{"_":21,"ana":22,"ref":23},"plaster on stone","#material.plaster","http://www.eagle-network.eu/voc/material/lod/126.html","",{"layout":26},{"rs":27,"damage":24},{"_":28,"ana":29,"ref":30},"painted","#execution.painted","http://www.eagle-network.eu/voc/writing/lod/10",{"lettering":32,"dimensions":33},"painted letters, simple in style without serifs and not perfectly following a horizontal line. Alpha has straight bar; theta is circular with a central point; M is very broad, all strokes diagonal, the mid-point not fully down to the lower line; sigma is lunate.",[34,39],{"type":35,"l":36,"from":37,"to":37,"unit":38},"letterHeight","Line 1","line1","mm",{"type":40,"l":41,"from":37,"to":42,"unit":38},"interlinear","Interlineation line 1 to 2","line2",{"_":44,"notBefore":45,"notAfter":46,"precision":47},"1st century BCE — 1st century CE",-100,100,"low",[49,53],{"_":50,"type":51,"ref":52},"Lilybaeum","ancient","http://pleiades.stoa.org/places/462281",{"_":54,"type":55,"ref":56},"Marsala","modern","http://sws.geonames.org/6542148",[58],[59,60],37.80355,12.4379,"Italy","Sicily",{"_":64,"role":65,"ref":66},"Museo archeologico regionale Lilibeo Marsala - Baglio Anselmi","museum","http://sicily.classics.ox.ac.uk/museum/108",{"type":68},"inventory",{"_":70,"mainLang":71,"languages":72},"Ancient Greek","grc",[70],{"n":74,"url":75,"height":76,"width":77,"desc":78,"surfaceType":79},"screen","ISic001550_tiled.tif","3680px","5520px","I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana","front",[],[82,82,83,84,85,86,87,88],"Supplementum epigraphicum graecum, 1923-","Manni Piraino, 1973, IGMusPalermo","Kretschmer, 1927, Das Femininum von ἥρως","Gabrici, 1929, Stele sepolcrali di Lilibeo a forma di Heroon","Bisi, 1970, Influenze italiote e siceliote sull'arte tardo-punica. Le stele funerarie di Lilibeo","Di Stefano, 1984, Lilibeo. Testimonianze archeologiche dal IV sec a.C. al V sec. d.C.","Vento, 2000, Le stele dipinte di Lilibeo",[90,90,91,92,93,94,95,96],"F2GG87EQ","F66S4X3M","NT9TNH4M","W9I8NZBC","2DZ9TJFH","Q5PB252W","RTAB9A28",[98,99,100,13,17,21,101,102,103,104,102,105,106,71],"isic001550","i.sicily inscription 001550",{"_":10},"lilybaeum","marsala","italy","sicily","museo archeologico regionale lilibeo marsala - baglio anselmi","ancient greek","\u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  \u003Ca id=\"al1-interpretive\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>Μαρία ἥρυς \u003Cbr id=\"al2-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">2\u003C/span>ἀγαθά \u003C/span>\u003C/div>  \u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>",{"author":109,"date":3,"citedRange":110,"ptr":111,"ref":113,"title":2,"citation":4},"Kretschmer","306 no.3",{"target":112},"http://zotero.org/groups/382445/items/NT9TNH4M",{"_":114,"target":114},"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002533",{"file":116,"uri":116,"title":117,"sta